Package: speedAnalyzerR
Type: Package
Title: Command-Line Eye-Tracking Analyzer (R)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Your", family = "Name", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "you@example.com"))
Description: Command-line tools to organize eye-tracking data into a BIDS-like layout, compute summaries, generate plots, and optionally render a simple video overlay from gaze data. No Python required.
